      "value": "<p>Your companion is a partially transformed blood wolf.</p>\n<p><strong>Size</strong> Small</p>\n<p><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> jaws (finesse), <strong>Damage</strong> 1d8 piercing</p>\n<p><strong>Str</strong> +2, <strong>Dex</strong> +3, <strong>Con</strong> +2, <strong>Int</strong> -4, <strong>Wis</strong> +1, <strong>Cha</strong> +0</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 8</p>\n<p><strong>Skill</strong> Intimidation</p>\n<p><strong>Senses</strong> darkvision, scent (imprecise, 30 feet)</p>\n<p><strong>Speed</strong> 40 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Support Benefit</strong> Your wolf tears tendons with each opening. Until the start of your next turn, your Strikes that damage creatures your wolf threatens give the target a -5-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 1 minute (-10 on a critical success).</p>\n<p><strong>Advanced Maneuver</strong> @Compendium[pf2e-animal-companions.AC-Advanced-Maneuvers.xssFjTXqGlsaddvl]{Knockdown}</p>"
